Post-Match Reflections: They know when they see us they don't like us, and I'm pretty sure they know we don't like them.
You seen the little brawl in between timeouts. It's always a great game. I love going against those guys. Plus they got the best player in the league, so I look forward to it.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Rudy Gobert and Christian Braun got into a scuffle resulting in double technical fouls after the Nuggets guard elevated for a poster dunk over Gobert.
Nikola Jokic added 26 points, 13 assists, and nine rebounds in the loss to Minnesota.
